custom-meta.meta-value: All data regarding HLA allele frequency is available from The Allele Frequency Net Database ( http://www.allelefrequencies.net/hla6006a.asp). Data can be downloaded by entering the ethnicity of interest as a search query. All protein sequences for H1N1 viral strains are available through UniProt ( http://www.uniprot.org/proteomes/). The proteome of each viral strain can be obtained by entering the strain name as a search query. All parameters calculated as a part of this work are within the paper and its Supporting Information files.
